<p>The speak command provides text to speech functionality. This provides a means to provide speech for content that you cannot pre-record. also it provides a very simple way for you to define small pieces of what ultimately could become complex IVR solutions. There is no need to pre-record any audio content for your service, unless you really want to.</p>

