I"Ñ<h1 id="bluevia-voice-and-sms-error-codes">BlueVia Voice and SMS Error Codes</h1>

<p>@todo add a complete list of known errors</p>
;T;@jI"/alpha/notifications/;T{;{	;I"ÈV<!DOCTYPE html>
