<p>There are several key differences between the BlueVia Voice API and existing BlueVia APIs.</p>

<p>Firstly BlueVia Voice APIs are not restricted for consumption to just Telefonica customers, this means that any phone can be used by you to engage with your customers globally. The APIs are not restricted to only be used by Telefonica customers, and they are not restricted only by mobile customers.</p>

