<p>The significant change for this demo can be found in the <em>startConfernece.php</em> code. In this case we are using the <a href="/alpha/commandref/record/"><em>record command</em></a> and the additional <em>conferenceProperies</em> element of <em>playOnEnter</em> this can be seen in either the moderator or participant code. Looking at the case for the moderator:</p>

