;T;
I"ê<h1 id="calls-resources">Calls Resources</h1>

<h2 id="calls-leg-collection">Calls Leg Collection</h2>

<pre><code> /comms/v1/calls/{callId}/legs{format}
</code></pre>

<p>No operations are allowed against the Call Legs Collection. This is as Call Legs are created by using the <a href="/alpha/commandref/dial/">dial command</a> or by creating an outbound call via a POST request to the <a href="/alpha/restref/calls/">calls resource</a>.</p>

<div class="apimethodgroup well well-small">
  <dl>
    <dt>POST</dt>
    <dd>NOT ALLOWED</dd>
  </dl>

</div>
<!-- apimethodgroup -->

<div class="apimethodgroup well well-small">
  <dl>
    <dt>GET</dt>
    <dd>NOT ALLOWED</dd>
  </dl>

</div>
<!-- apimethodgroup -->

<div class="apimethodgroup well well-small">
  <dl>
    <dt>PUT</dt>
    <dd>NOT ALLOWED</dd>
  </dl>

</div>
<!-- apimethodgroup -->

<div class="apimethodgroup well well-small">
  <dl>
    <dt>DELETE</dt>
    <dd>NOT ALLOWED</dd>
  </dl>

</div>
<!-- apimethodgroup -->

