<h2 id="call-leg-statuses">Call Leg Statuses</h2>

<p>The possible call leg statuses are:</p>

<ul>
<li>
<em>ringing</em> - the destination of this call leg is ringing</li>
  <li>
<em>connected</em> - the call leg is established</li>
  <li>
<em>onhold</em> - the call leg is on hold</li>
  <li>
<em>terminated</em> - a once connected call leg has finished.</li>
</ul>
<hr>
