;T;	I"ˇ## Call Leg Statuses

The possible call leg statuses are:

* *ringing* - the destination of this call leg is ringing
* *connected* - the call leg is established
* *onhold* - the call leg is on hold
* *terminated* - a once connected call leg has finished.
;T;
I"n<h2 id="call-leg-statuses">Call Leg Statuses</h2>

<p>The possible call leg statuses are:</p>

<ul>
  <li><em>ringing</em> - the destination of this call leg is ringing</li>
  <li><em>connected</em> - the call leg is established</li>
  <li><em>onhold</em> - the call leg is on hold</li>
  <li><em>terminated</em> - a once connected call leg has finished.</li>
</ul>
