<h1 id="call-statuses">Call Statuses</h1>

<p>The Status of a call is dependant on the state of the call legs contained within the call. The following call statuses are available:</p>

<ul>
<li>
<em>connecting</em> - the call is being created. At this stage no calls legs have been connected </li>
  <li>
<em>established</em> - the call is ongoing. In this state at least one leg is connected to the call</li>
  <li>
<em>terminated</em> - the call is terminated. A call that had been established is now finished</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<span id="prevPage" class="bottomLinks pull-left"></span>
        <span id="nextPage" class="bottomLinks pull-right"></span>

