;T;	I"Æ# Call Statuses

The Status of a call is dependant on the state of the call legs contained within the call. The following call statuses are available:

* *connecting* - the call is being created. At this stage no calls legs have been connected 
* *established* - the call is ongoing. In this state at least one leg is connected to the call
* *terminated* - the call is terminated. A call that had been established is now finished
;T;
I"
<h1 id="call-statuses">Call Statuses</h1>

<p>The Status of a call is dependant on the state of the call legs contained within the call. The following call statuses are available:</p>

<ul>
  <li><em>connecting</em> - the call is being created. At this stage no calls legs have been connected </li>
  <li><em>established</em> - the call is ongoing. In this state at least one leg is connected to the call</li>
  <li><em>terminated</em> - the call is terminated. A call that had been established is now finished</li>
</ul>
