<h1 id="account-management-resources">Account Management Resources</h1>

<h2 id="recordings">Recordings</h2>

<pre><code> URI  Not defined for alpha
</code></pre>

<div class="apimethodgroup well">

  <p>As highlighted in the <a href="../../overview/knownlimitations/">Known Limitations</a> during the alpha period it will not be possible to persist recordings on BlueVia. There are solutions provided to export these <a href="../../commandref/record/">to export your recordings</a> to your own hosting solution. When available the Recordings resource will allow you to access and manage recordings hosted by BlueVia </p>

  <!-- This HTML doesn't need changes -->
</div>
