<h1 id="rest-api-requests">REST API Requests</h1>

<p>Requests made to the BlueVia Voice RESTful API require HTTP Basic Authentication:</p>

<ul>
<li>your username is your <em>BlueVia Voice API Key</em>
</li>
  <li>your password is your <em>BlueVia Voice API Secret</em>
</li>
</ul>
<p>Both of these are available on your BlueVia Dashboard, once you have logged into the BlueVia Portal.</p>

        <hr>
