<h1 id="resources">Resources</h1>

<p>The alpha release of the BlueVia RESTful API, as described by the <a href="../">resource tree</a> covers :</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="../accountresources/">Account management</a></li>
  <li><a href="../availablenumberscollection/">Available Numbers</a></li>
  <li>
<a href="../calls/">Calls</a> and</li>
  <li><a href="../sms/">SMS</a></li>
</ul>
<p>NOTE: The alpha API does not represent the final RESTful AI that will be made available by the BlueVIa Voice APIs. Further resource access is being made available. Resources that are not available in the alpha release are highlighted below.</p>

